00:11:43.370 --> 00:11:46.770 align:middle line:84%
and I was trying to tell
him that he was wrong.

00:11:46.770 --> 00:11:51.870 align:middle line:84%
>>I could see the soldiers and
the nurses and the doctors,

00:11:51.870 --> 00:11:53.710 align:middle line:90%
but they could not see me.

00:11:53.710 --> 00:11:55.820 align:middle line:84%
And I went from
ward to ward, bed

00:11:55.820 --> 00:11:59.260 align:middle line:84%
to bed trying to find a
soldier that I thought

00:11:59.260 --> 00:12:01.000 align:middle line:84%
that looked like me
lying in the bed.

00:12:01.000 --> 00:12:03.382 align:middle line:84%
Was becoming more and more
desperate because, as I say,

00:12:03.382 --> 00:12:05.340 align:middle line:84%
