00:12:06.390 --> 00:12:11.260 align:middle line:84%
I finally went into this
little isolated ward room.

00:12:11.260 --> 00:12:13.670 align:middle line:84%
And sure enough, lying in the
bed with a sheet pulled up

00:12:13.670 --> 00:12:17.330 align:middle line:84%
