this body that I

00:12:17.330 --> 00:12:18.730 align:middle line:84%
had to recognize
as me because it

00:12:18.730 --> 00:12:20.750 align:middle line:84%
had my fraternity
ring on its finger.

00:12:20.750 --> 00:12:23.500 align:middle line:84%
>>And there was this
slight buzzing at the ear,

00:12:23.500 --> 00:12:26.540 align:middle line:84%
and at felt myself
pop out of the body.

00:12:26.540 --> 00:12:29.670 align:middle line:84%
I was-- I don't
know how I came out.

00:12:29.670 --> 00:12:32.800 align:middle line:84%
I was just suddenly
out of the body.

00:12:32.800 --> 00:12:36.040 align:middle line:84%
And I sat down on the
head of the bed a minute

00:12:36.040 --> 00:12:37.500 align:middle line:90%
