00:12:41.340 --> 00:12:43.570 align:middle line:90%
And he said, she's gone.

00:12:43.570 --> 00:12:44.730 align:middle line:90%
And I couldn't believe it.

00:12:44.730 --> 00:12:46.021 align:middle line:90%
And I thought well, who's gone?

00:12:46.021 --> 00:12:48.730 align:middle line:84%
